---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Scenarios" description="SAPIEN scenario library — calibrated multi-turn conversations for testing AI behavioral integrity.">
  <section class="hero-sm">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge">Scenario Library</span>
      <h1>Scenarios</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        The scenario library is being migrated to the new site. In the meantime, <a href="/glossary/#scenario" class="key-term" data-definition="A scripted multi-turn conversation testing model behavioral safety.">scenarios</a> are documented within each module specification.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <a href="/modules/sycophantic-drift/" class="link-arrow">View Sycophantic Drift scenarios &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Definition block -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="definition-block">
        <h2>What is a Scenario?</h2>
        <p>A <strong>scenario</strong> is a scripted <a href="/glossary/#multi-turn-conversation" class="key-term" data-definition="A back-and-forth exchange with an AI model across multiple messages, where the model can reference earlier messages.">multi-turn conversation</a> designed to test whether an AI model maintains its safety boundaries under realistic conversational pressure. Each scenario has an opening prompt (a reasonable user question), followed by <a href="/glossary/#escalation" class="key-term" data-definition="A pressure turn in a scenario designed to increase conversational pressure.">escalation</a> turns that apply increasing pressure using calibrated <a href="/glossary/#pressure-technique" class="key-term" data-definition="One of 14 catalogued conversational pressure methods (SP-T001 through SP-T014).">techniques</a>. The model's responses are scored across four behavioral <a href="/glossary/#dimension" class="key-term" data-definition="One of four scored behavioral measurements: Specificity, Risk Disclosure, Epistemic, Emotional.">dimensions</a> at each turn.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Anatomy of a scenario -->
      <div class="anatomy">
        <h3>Anatomy of a Scenario</h3>
        <div class="anatomy-flow">
          <div class="anatomy-phase">
            <span class="anatomy-label">Opening</span>
            <span class="anatomy-desc">Reasonable user question</span>
          </div>
          <div class="anatomy-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="anatomy-phase anatomy-phase-optional">
            <span class="anatomy-label">Rapport</span>
            <span class="anatomy-desc">Optional trust-building</span>
          </div>
          <div class="anatomy-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="anatomy-phase">
            <span class="anatomy-label">Escalation 1</span>
            <span class="anatomy-desc">Light pressure applied</span>
          </div>
          <div class="anatomy-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="anatomy-phase">
            <span class="anatomy-label">Escalation 2</span>
            <span class="anatomy-desc">Increased pressure</span>
          </div>
          <div class="anatomy-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="anatomy-phase anatomy-phase-final">
            <span class="anatomy-label">Final Turn</span>
            <span class="anatomy-desc">Maximum pressure</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <h2>Contribute Scenarios</h2>
        <p>
          Help expand the SAPIEN scenario library. We accept community-authored scenarios that pass the
          <a href="/framework/scenarios/">quality rubric</a> and cover new domains or pressure patterns.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/sapiencallenmajin/TheSAPIENFramework" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn">
          Contribute on GitHub &nearr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-sm {
    padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .hero-sm h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 640px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .link-arrow {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .link-arrow:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .cta-card {
    background: #F8F9FA;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }
  .cta-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .cta-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .cta-card a:not(.btn) {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-navy);
    color: #FFFFFF;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn:hover {
    background: var(--color-slate);
    color: #FFFFFF;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* Definition block */
  .definition-block {
    background: #F8F9FA;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .definition-block h2 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .definition-block p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 52rem;
  }

  /* Anatomy of a scenario */
  .anatomy {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .anatomy h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .anatomy-flow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .anatomy-phase {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 110px;
  }
  .anatomy-phase-optional {
    border-style: dashed;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }
  .anatomy-phase-final {
    border-color: #EA580C;
    background: #FFF7ED;
  }
  .anatomy-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .anatomy-desc {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }
  .anatomy-arrow {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 3;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .anatomy-flow {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    .anatomy-arrow {
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1;
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
  }
</style>
